OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry but rather cloudy,
OL,6,Falthough the odd spot of early light
OL,7,Frain cannot be ruled out across
OL,8,Fnorthwestern hills. Best of any sunny
OL,9,Fspells in the south and east at first,
OL,10,Fbut some brighter spells possible for
OL,11,Fall throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry evening, before thicker
OL,14,Fcloud spreads south. Most parts
OL,15,Fstaying dry, but this could bring some
OL,16,Fbrief light rain. Further clear spells
OL,17,Ffollow after midnight, but winds also
OL,18,Fstrengthening slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
